{"tid":347343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人已經慣曬一個人","createTime":"2017-08-04T17:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T19:29:47.000Z","uid":561,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"771e143ef90050221e8a033049aa28508f247a68","tid":347343,"uid":561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:37:19.000Z","msg":"以前中學大學日日要一大班人圍威喂先開心<br />\n返學約埋一齊 食飯一齊 放學返完屋企都再約出黎食飯<br />\n<br />\n到出黎做野 係忙 但都唔係無時間<br />\n佢地一大班人約出黎我都唔會再出去<br />\n唔知點解唔想再去維繫同其他人既關係<br />\n返工工種問題可以成日去其他地方逗留<br />\n同事問出唔出去 通常都唔出 自己留起酒店做下尖 訓下覺 自己一個出去唱k同打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪好正常定我有社交問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37380e5d0fa206a7b311292e071b8d3fcffc64e","tid":347343,"uid":28624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:42:43.000Z","msg":"日日都係得自己過<br />\n行街食飯睇戲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9501ef5aa361c15fd7c894adf1e504990a642384","tid":347343,"uid":129509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:54:48.000Z","msg":"我都係，明明冇人約都唔想出<br />\n覺得自己一個更開心"},{"pid":"7779ee689f548c3a928a72a35c470611a1f00a19","tid":347343,"uid":129509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係，明明<span style=\"color: red;\">有</span>人約都唔想出<br />\n覺得自己一個更開心</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e24c47fb32773863d8a97e0b789bed905b41f49c","tid":347343,"uid":561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:55:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日都係得自己過<br />\n行街食飯睇戲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果個毒撚表我差自己露營未試過 其他做齊曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.